title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 4 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 4 2022
description:
Arizona AG Mark Brnovich joins Clay and Buck to discuss the disaster coming at the border and why he's running for Senate. It's been one year since the CDC director said the vaccine would prevent you from getting and spreading covid. C&B analyze the latest on the war in Ukraine. Chuck Todd says running for president might be "too much work" for Trump.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
